graph LR
    User([End User]) --> |Web Access| App(React Application)
    
    subgraph Web Frontend
        App --> State[React State]
        App --> Auth[Auth Context]
        App --> Views[Dashboard / Library / Admin]
    end
    
    Views -->|HTTP POST| API(FastAPI Server)
    
    subgraph Backend Server
        API --> AuthMW[Role Middleware]
        API --> AudioModule[Audio Hashing]
        API --> VideoModule[Video Hashing]
        API --> MatchModule[Scoring Engine]
    end
    
    subgraph Data Storage
        AudioModule --> DB[(PostgreSQL)]
        VideoModule --> DB
        MatchModule --> DB
        MatchModule --> BKTree[BK-Tree Index]
    end
